rComments: She is so helpful and encouraging. Very understanding of an undergrad student's stressful life. As long as you are respectful (for example, letting her know ahead that you'll be leaving class early), she will understand and appreciate it a lot.

She is an amazing and funny prof. i would definitely recommend her, she loves what she does, and does not move on until everyone understands what she is explaining especially because it is a language course. Very understanding, approachable, very fair with marks and tests. One of my best prof's

This woman is hilarious!  This is an easy class as long as you attend the lectures!  She makes things very easy to understand :)  I plan on continuing italian because of her!  I sure hope she teaches it next year!  Ah, she's great :)
Breat teacher, marks tests and quizes quickly and isvery helpful. Constantly asks if anyone doesn't understand, will not go on to the next topic until everyone in the class understands.
